title: Kombilife Ben
description: This week we're joined by ben from KombiLife.com (@HastaAlaska).  Ben hales from the Isle of Jersey and has set out on a journey to travel from Chile to Alaska in a Volkswagen Bus (aka Kombi). Ben did not disappoint with tales of his long journey and the road ahead in what has become an exceptional story.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
